    public class LoggingPropertyOracle<I,​A extends net.automatalib.automaton.concept.Output<I,​D>,​P,​D>
extends Object
implements PropertyOracle<I,​A,​P,​D>
    A PropertyOracle that performs logging.

    This class will log whenever the property is disproved, or when a counterexample to an automaton is found (i.e. a spurious counterexample is found).
